# Privacy Policy  

**Effective Date:** 15/02/2025  

Thank you for using Bible for all. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information.  

## 📌 Information We Do Not Collect  
We respect your privacy. **Bible for all.** does not:  
- ❌ Collect any **personal information** such as name, email, or phone number.  
- ❌ Store or track **your activity** within the app.  
- ❌ Use third-party APIs to collect or process your data.  

## 📌 Third-Party Services  
Our app uses **Google AdMob** to display advertisements. **AdMob may collect and use device information** to show relevant ads. This data collection is managed by Google, and you can review their privacy policy here:  
👉 [Google AdMob Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads)  

## 📌 How We Ensure Privacy  
✔️ We **do not store any data** on our servers.  
✔️ We **do not track your behavior** or collect analytics.  
✔️ We **only use Google AdMob**, which operates independently under Google’s privacy terms.  

## 📌 Changes to This Policy  
We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be posted in the app or on our GitHub repository.  

## 📌 Contact Us  
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:  
📧 developer.queenbee@gmail.com  
